377
00:18:22,309 --> 00:18:23,435
[farting]

378
00:18:25,229 --> 00:18:26,563
Yeah, I don't like this.

379
00:18:26,647 --> 00:18:27,773
Fair enough.

380
00:18:30,901 --> 00:18:32,027
Here.

381
00:18:32,111 --> 00:18:34,404
