382
00:18:34,488 --> 00:18:37,449
Devi might've been
the worst runner I've ever seen,

383
00:18:37,533 --> 00:18:41,078
but she truly was
the Usain Bolt of cockblocking.

384
00:18:41,161 --> 00:18:43,914
No way were these two making it
to Trent's tent

385
00:18:43,997 --> 00:18:45,707
