-Where you been?

434
00:21:21,697 --> 00:21:24,950
I was trying to study,
but Trent got me loose.

435
00:21:25,033 --> 00:21:26,201
[laughs]

436
00:21:26,827 --> 00:21:30,247
But don't worry. I'm ready
to learn the shit out of this shit.

437
00:21:32,332 --> 00:21:33,625
