438
00:21:37,296 --> 00:21:38,922
[upbeat music playing]

439
00:21:40,382 --> 00:21:41,717
[birds chirping]

440
00:21:43,635 --> 00:21:44,761
[yawning]

441
00:21:44,845 --> 00:21:46,596
[sobbing]

442
00:21:48,682 --> 00:21:52,728
