They're saying I have an eating disorder.

444
00:22:00,110 --> 00:22:02,070
Really? That's terrible.

445
00:22:02,612 --> 00:22:05,741
But hey, it's just a rumor, right?

446
00:22:05,824 --> 00:22:08,493
Whoever said that
